---
title: Tuscan Ribollita with Kale, Italian Sausage, and Parmesan Croutons
description: Our take on the beloved Ribollita is ideal for this time of year. Sweet Italian sausage adds intense flavor to the dish, but our favorite addition is the cheesy croutons—perfect for soaking up all that yummy broth!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5654ab3c79a23c43138b4567.jpg
